snippet.textDisplay: Is this really the standard Coke Studio India is aiming for now? While Anuv Jain is undoubtedly my fav artist too, but this particular sing feels more like one of his regular single releases than a Coke Studio production. The composition and lyrics seem rather ordinary, and it’s hard to find that distinctiveness which usually sets Coke Studio apart.
